headline: Should You Forget Coca-Cola? Why These Unstoppable Stocks Are Better Buys.
summary: There's nothing wrong with Coca-Cola (NYSE: KO) as a company.  Coke's biggest strength is that it is a dominant beverage maker.  At the end of the day, beverages are just one tiny niche of the broader consumer staples sector.
